data.description: 9.02 acres, has 2 springs that I know of and 2 well casings on the property. Central heat and air. 12x20 shed, chicken coop, over sized dog kennel, and at the moment that start of a 12x30 garage on a poured concrete slab. Plenty of usable land. Mostly wooded property. Large garden already in use. Has an above ground pool just recently put in. And much more......its a beautiful piece of property. Has fiber internet access. Great for hunting. Has creeks on the lower part of the property. 4 bedroom 2 bath with a bonus room. Also has a back access driveway to the property as well. Only serious inquiries please. If it's still listed it is still available. Reduced price for quick sale. Wont stay long at this price.
